text: Eunidia quadrivittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1938. It is known from Kenya and Somalia.BioLib.cz - Eunidia quadrivittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1938
title: Eunidia quadrivittata
